reviews.text: Decent little station, a single train runs back and forth between greenford and west ealing. as theres only one train on such a short track you may as well get on going the wrong direction if you miss your train as it will be warmer on board and rather than waiting in the cold for the same train to return. trains usually run on time. no sunday service though. some of the lights not working so take care on the steps. no ticket office or ticket machines.
